snippet: Duke finally had all the players that made the Blue Devils the top-ranked team in the preseason — except that, for most of the night, they didn't play like it....
lead_paragraph: Duke finally had all the players that made the Blue Devils the top-ranked team in the preseason — except that, for most of the night, they didn't play like it.
